Sing it from the mountains, we have a new Tech Editor!
{pp}
We welcome Shane Ponting as our new Tech Editor.  Not only will he
writeon whatever technological Amigan subject comes to his mind (and he
{italic}does{noitalic} take requests), but feel free to write in with
your questions and we'll see if he can answer them (come on, challenge
him).  As far as his pertinent background, consider the following:
{pp}
Amiga CV:{p}
iBrowse 2.3 and 3.0 beta-tester{p}
OS4.0 Beta tester{p}
Virus Executor beta tester{p}
Taranaki Regional amiga Technician{p}
A+ Certified CompTIA training atm{p}
NZQA Certificate in Computing Levels 2&3, considering 4
{pp}
Enough qualifications for you?  Welcome aboard Shane!
{pp}
